                  style: TextStyle(
                      fontSize: 10,
                      color: AgriColors.green4,
                      letterSpacing: 0.5)),
            ],
          ),
          Container(
            margin: const EdgeInsets.only(left: 6),
            padding: const EdgeInsets.symmetric(horizontal: 7, vertical: 2),
            decoration: BoxDecoration(
              color: AgriColors.straw,
              borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(12),
